										</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="control is-spaced has-wrap is-aligned-start">
									<div class="control-left">
										<p class="is-bold">
											Categories
										</p>
									</div>
									<div class="control-right">
										<p class="has-text-right">
											SAAS, Start Up, Business, Branding, Company, Fun, Leisure, Domains, Healthcare
										</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="control is-grouped">
									<div id="make-offer-button" class="control is-expanded">
										<a class="button is-stylish is-fullwidth is-primary">Make Offer</a>
